    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can call <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/awt/Window.html#setLocationRelativeTo-java.awt.Component-\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>JFrame.setLocationRelativeTo(null)</code></a> to center the window. Make sure to put this before <code>JFrame.setVisible(true)</code></p>\n"
