      "profile_image" : "https://graph.facebook.com/10155412882505230/picture?type=large",
      "display_name" : "Kingsley Ijike",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/4734280/kingsley-ijike"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1427811385,
    "creation_date" : 1427811385,
    "answer_id" : 29370782,
    "question_id" : 2442599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you use NetBeans, simply click on the frame on the design view, then the code tab on its properties. Next, check 'Generate Center'. That will get the job done.</p>\n"
