    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use this method, which allows the JFrame to be centered and full screen at the same time.</p>\n\n<pre><code>yourframe.setExtendedState(JFrame.MAXIMIZED_BOTH);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "user_type" : "does_not_exist",
      "display_name" : "user7205283"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
