    "creation_date" : 1480937509,
    "answer_id" : 40973298,
    "question_id" : 2442599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you explicitly <code>setPreferredSize(new Dimension(X, Y));</code> then it is better to use:</p>\n\n<p><code>setLocation(dim.width/2-this.getPreferredSize().width/2, dim.height/2-this.getPreferredSize().height/2);</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 15173731,
      "reputation" : 11,
      "user_id" : 10949040,
      "user_type" : "unregistered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3e6be5869455deecf4faebc96261afef?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "K V Ramana",
