  "title" : "How to set JFrame to appear centered, regardless of monitor resolution?",
  "body" : "<p>While working with Java, I find it hard to position my main window in the center of the screen when I start the application.</p>\n\n<p>Is there any way I can do that?\nIt doesn't have to be vertically centered, horizontal alignment is the more important goal for me. But vertical alignment is also welcome.</p>\n"
